@caprastro @WWU I know the answer at @UW is (as they said today) they handle thousands of grant submissions per year, and so I guess that level of service doesn't scale?... which I find unsatisfying. So we have dept folks try to fill the gaps, but can't do it all

@caprastro I greatly miss the grant management experience from my prev. university (@WWU). They provided end-to-end support with a truly personal touch. I worked with ONE person almost entirely, from drawing up budget to submission, and it was wonderful

I don’t know what @WWU student needs to hear this (I did!) but our Executive Director of Counseling, Health and Wellness center @DrSis is a WOC and after sobbing through her video message on Front Page I am effectively touched and feeling slightly better about being at #WWU 🖤
